messages.message: I'm planning on running a bunch of files through process_files (around 740 pdfs, 1300 total pages) , do I need to break that up into batches or will running the flow on all at once be fine? I'd probably run this tonight/this weekend on instabase.com (http://instabase.com)

it’ll be fine, as long as you run with flow V2 (make sure “flow -> tools -> compile” works fine, if it can’t compile, the flow will default to Flow V1 which will stop anyone else’s jobs from running until all of yours finish).
